{"tid":1567572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有關連儂牆一事","createTime":"2019-09-14T06:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T14:30:21.000Z","uid":128190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d9168bdff4f3e1b5697c880fe8f46710bfa6ab1","tid":1567572,"uid":128190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"各位手足，在此千叮萬囑大家，係人數/情況無優勢嘅情況下唔好上前拍片同阻止。<br />\n<br />\n第一，就算比你影到佢地個樣又點？<br />\n第二，佢地打你係唔會比人拉，你只可以硬食。<br />\n<br />\n所以，只可以係有人數/情況優勢嘅情況下先上前，同埋你一定要有心理準備開拖，至少都有返個口罩遮樣，如果無請離開，搵日再去修復就算。<br />\n<br />\n記住，誰大誰惡誰正確，唔明呢個道理/無呢個決心就唔好上前。"},{"pid":"98f6491c453586929fb68666d4246029f10c46da","tid":1567572,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:24:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e65bd4e49812cae522d8ab73c21002b904ec2ac","tid":1567572,"uid":128190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"915！"},{"pid":"dfcafac09395caf74b6ab790b56c11e5b23cc517","tid":1567572,"uid":320472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"小心依班人清場...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/youthcleaning\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyouthcleaning&d=CilPfclB3esq2v